3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) is another possible category as the paper focuses on enhancing safety and reliability in vehicular communication systems. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper mentions the possibility of vehicle-to-pedestrian communication in C-V2X. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also a less likely category, but still possible as the paper briefly mentions the need for enhanced security in C-V2X networks.
